---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Does Democracy Apply to Okinawa? | Unmuting Ryukyu">

	<!-- ARTICLE HEADER -->
	<header style="background:#272736;padding:120px 32px 80px;position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-bottom:1px solid #3a3a5a;">
		<!-- Background Blur Suggestion -->
		<div style="position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(circle at 50% 50%, rgba(201,48,44,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);z-index:0;"></div>
		
		<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;z-index:1;">
			<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:32px;">
				<span style="display:inline-block;background:#c9302c;color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;padding:6px 16px;border-radius:2px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;">Documentary Analysis</span>
				<span style="color:#666666;font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:14px;">March 9, 2026</span>
			</div>
			
			<h1 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,6vw,56px);font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:0 0 24px 0;line-height:1.1;letter-spacing:-0.02em;">Does Democracy Apply to Okinawa?<br/><span style="color:#c8a951;">The Henoko Base Issue</span></h1>
			
			<p style="color:#9ca3af;font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:20px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 40px 0;max-width:600px;">When the will of 72% of the people is ignored, can we still call it a decision?</p>

			<div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
				<div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:#c8a951;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#272736;font-weight:800;font-size:12px;">ST</div>
				<div>
					<p style="color:#f5f0e8;font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;margin:0;">Shohei Toguchi</p>
					<p style="color:#666666;font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:12px;margin:0;">Filmmaker & Researcher</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</header>

	<!-- ARTICLE CONTENT -->
	<article style="background:#272736;padding:80px 32px 120px;">
		<div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
			
			<!-- Video Embed -->
			<div style="background:#000;border:1px solid #3a3a5a;margin-bottom:64px;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);">
				<div style="position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;height:0;">
					<iframe style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;border:0;" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/placeholder" title="Does Democracy Apply to Okinawa?" allow="accelerometer;autoplay;clipboard-write;encrypted-media;gyroscope;picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe>
				</div>
                <div style="padding:20px;background:#2d2d50;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;">
                    <p style="color:#9ca3af;font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:13px;margin:0;">Watch the documentary on YouTube</p>
                    <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@letsgokinawa" style="color:#c8a951;font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:13px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;">Watch more →</a>
                </div>
			</div>

			<div style="font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:18px;line-height:2;color:#f5f0e8;">
				
				<p style="margin-bottom:40px;font-weight:500;color:#c8a951;font-size:22px;line-height:1.6;">There is a place where democracy doesn’t apply in Japan. This is Okinawa.</p>

				<h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:80px 0 32px 0;border-left:4px solid #c9302c;padding-left:24px;">The Ignored Referendum</h2>
				<p style="margin-bottom:32px;">In 2019, a prefectural referendum was held over the construction of the new Henoko base. Over 72% of the voters—about 430,000 Okinawans—said "No." With 70% of all US military bases in Japan concentrated here, it was a desperate cry: "We don't need any more bases."</p>
				
				<blockquote style="margin:48px 0;padding:32px;background:#2d2d50;border-left:4px solid #c8a951;font-style:italic;color:#c8a951;">
					"Our will was shown, but it was not treated as a decision."
				</blockquote>

				<p style="margin-bottom:32px;">Yet, the plan didn't stop. The national government bypassed local authorities to force it through—an unprecedented move. It brought into question whether local autonomy is protected at all.</p>

				<h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:80px 0 32px 0;border-left:4px solid #c9302c;padding-left:24px;">A Strategic Sacrifice</h2>
				<p style="margin-bottom:32px;">We were once the independent Ryukyu Kingdom. We had our own language, our own culture, and a life lived with the land and the sea. But Okinawa was taken over. And during WWII, without any decision-making power, we were placed on the absolute frontlines as a strategic sacrifice. As a result, one in four Okinawans lost their lives.</p>

				<h2 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:32px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin:80px 0 32px 0;border-left:4px solid #c9302c;padding-left:24px;">The Present Reality</h2>
				<p style="margin-bottom:32px;">Even after the war, the structure where our voices are ignored in decisions has continued. It hasn't changed today. If war breaks out again, the very first battlefield will become here in Okinawa.</p>
				<p style="margin-bottom:32px;">When speaking up isn't heard, and voting changes nothing... that accumulation breeds resignation even before anger.</p>

				<div style="margin-top:100px;padding:60px 40px;background:#2d2d50;border:1px solid #3a3a5a;text-align:center;border-radius:4px;">
					<h3 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:28px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin-bottom:24px;">Can we still call this a democracy?</h3>
					<p style="color:#9ca3af;margin-bottom:32px;">Okinawa is the place where majority rule does not function. Please, think about this just once... as a story about your very own hometown.</p>
					<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@letsgokinawa" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration:none;color:#c8a951;font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-weight:700;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:1px solid #c8a951;padding-bottom:2px;">Watch on YouTube →</a>
				</div>

				<div style="margin-top:80px;border-top:1px solid #3a3a5a;padding-top:40px;">
					<p style="color:#666666;font-family:'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;">
						※この記事は2026年3月9日のドキュメンタリー台本に基づいています。<br/>
						Okinawa, where majority rule does not function. When showing your will, and making a decision, become two completely different things.
					</p>
				</div>

			</div>
		</div>
	</article>

    <!-- RELATED POSTS -->
    <section style="padding:100px 32px;background:#2d2d50;border-top:1px solid #3a3a5a;">
        <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;">
            <h3 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:20px;font-weight:800;color:#f5f0e8;margin-bottom:40px;">Related Stories</h3>
            <a href="/blog/battle-of-okinawa/" style="text-decoration:none;display:flex;gap:24px;align-items:center;background:#272736;padding:24px;border:1px solid #3a3a5a;border-radius:4px;">
                <div style="width:120px;height:80px;background:#333;flex-shrink:0;border-radius:2px;overflow:hidden;">
                    <img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/2v2vOrz5RXA/hqdefault.jpg" alt="Battle of Okinawa" style="width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;opacity:0.7;"/>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h4 style="font-family:'DM Sans', sans-serif;font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#f5f0e8;margin:0 0 8px 0;">10 Realities of the Battle of Okinawa</h4>
                    <p style="color:#9ca3af;font-family:'Inter', sans-serif;font-size:14px;margin:0;">Exploring the "Typhoon of Steel" and its lasting impact.</p>
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</Layout>
